(30,7,'2009-11-02 18:35:16','2009-11-02 16:35:16','Raw Shaping Form Finding landed a platform! The ICSID World Design Congress 2009 in Singapore! [50th anniversary 1959-2009 of ICSID]\n\nLatest news:\n\nRSFF is presented and being received very well by the expert audience ! We invite and welcome serious industry partners to work with us and share knowledge, expertise and intuive interactions! We are also looking for sponsorship or possible project investors from industries or other interested parties.\n\nYesterdays\' news:\n\nFollow this link for the program: <a href=\"http://www.icsidcongress09.com/website/education.asp\">http://www.icsidcongress09.com/website/education.asp</a>\n\nEarlier news:\n\nThe Raw Shaping Society will present their paper:  \'Bridging the Design Gap: Towards an Intuitive Design Tool\' at the ICSID World Design Congress in Singapore 2009.','Raw Shaping Form Finding in Singapore! 2009','','publish','open','open','','raw-shaping-form-finding-goes-to-singapore','','','2009-11-02 18:35:16','2009-11-02 16:35:16','',0,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=30',0,'post','',0),
(40,7,'2009-11-09 18:42:31','2009-11-09 16:42:31','Home of the Raw Shaping Form Finding Society.\n\nHave a go at our research, experimentation and development of  intuitive design tools to assist designers, engineers, architects and artists in externalization, shape ideation and iteratively creating their ideas and/or fuzzy notions into real tangible and virtual real representations.\n\n<em>Click on image to play movie:</em>\n\nRSFF Hybrid Design Tool\n[vimeo 43850666]\n\nLFDS Hybrid Design Tool\n\n[vimeo 13462411]\n\nLFDS in Education@UTwente\n\n[vimeo 24275139]\nOur ongoing experimentations and embedding of intuitive design assignments in design education allow us to [re]search for new applications and innovations in design tools.\n\nFurther knowledge acquisition is derived from distributed cognitive  interaction during tangible experiments. The hands are the instruments of the mind.\n\nEnjoy! RSFF: Hybrid Design Tool - Winner of the Laval Virtual Award 2010 for Design  + Simulation','Rawshaping Technology heuristic shape ideation','','publish','open','open','','welcome','','','2009-11-09 18:42:31','2009-11-09 16:42:31','',0,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=40',0,'post','',0),
