(1024,7,'2013-02-06 21:18:25','2013-02-06 19:18:25','First ever Hackathon organized at University of Twente for students of three different faculties; Information Technology | Industrial Design Engineering | Creative Technology to collaboratively build a product in 24 hours. This multi-disciplinary hackathon is sponsored by Phusion and Rawshaping Technology to make this exiting event possible. Students will work on their product in teams of 3 and work for 24 hours on end. The theme will be “Smart Surroundings” for example apps and devices for everyday use.\n\nThe event starts on 18:00 PM at Thursday February 7th, 2013 until Friday the 8th of February, 18:00 PM.\n\nMain sponsor: <a href=\"http://www.phusion.nl\">www.phusion.nl</a>\n\nOrganizers:  Interactief Student Organization | Phusion BV | Rawshaping Technology\n\nWith kind support of University of Twente, the Netherlands.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;','Hackathon 2013 @ UTwente','','publish','open','open','','hackathon-utwente','','','2013-02-06 21:18:25','2013-02-06 19:18:25','',0,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=1024',0,'post','',0),
