(1416,7,'2013-02-13 13:37:36','2013-02-13 11:37:36','Enjoy some images of the epic Hackathon@UTwente, organized by Phusion, InterActief and Rawshaping Technology;\n\nFor a dynamic cinematic impression:\n\n<a title=\"Hackaton 2013\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=kcPTGKYKlfw\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=kcPTGKYKlfw</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack01.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack02.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack03.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack04.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack05.jpg\" />\n\nIt was Priceless!\n\n#1 Infinity Game by Marcel Goethals and Robbert de Vries\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%201st%20pr.jpg\" />\n\n#2 SwipeMeister App by Wessel de Vries, Jonathan Juursema and Sefrijn Langen\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%202nd%20pr.jpg\" />\n\n#3 JeMoeder App by Derek Cardol, Fabian Dijkstra, Bas Veeling and Dennis Martina\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%203rd%20pr.jpg\" />\n\n#4 RuisBuis App by Marijn Romeijn, Ruben Kruiper and Kostas Drakonakis\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%204th%20pr.jpg\" />\n\n#5 EenGoedGesprek App by Leon Spikker, Lennart Buit and Joost van Doorn\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%205th%20pr.jpg\" />\n\n#6 GoingDutch App by Sanne Wolbers, Anne-Loes Barends, Thijs Schepers and Emile Nijssen\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hack%206th%20pr.jpg\" />\n\nPhotography by Robert Wendrich © 2013','Hackathon 2013 MashUp After 24H','','inherit','open','open','','1030-revision','','','2013-02-13 13:37:36',