(1422,7,'2011-06-22 16:38:59','2011-06-22 14:38:59','On Saturday June 25th, 2011 we will bring the LFDS to market. Embedding Design In Life. This cultural art &amp; design event will take place in Breukelen (Brooklyn) and start at 11:00 AM. Location is a beautiful parc in the center of town named Boom&amp;Bosch.\n\nWe are very curious and interested to see how the general public will react to our Loosely Fitted Design Synthesizer. Everybody who wants to try is welcome to make iterations and familiarize him/herself with the hybrid design tool. As a token of appreciation we will print one iteration by choice on a postcard as a memorabilia.\n\nTo keep the marketing objectified we will not convey that we are researchers or rawshapers.','Market Research ','','inherit','open','open','','794-revision','','','2011-06-22 16:38:59','2011-06-22 14:38:59','',794,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=1422',0,'revision','',0),
