(1436,7,'2013-03-28 12:43:52','2013-03-28 12:43:52','One of the first films made as a cooperation between Daniel Poolen and Robert Wendrich.  In this movie we played with the many DS iterations that were  made by first year students during Formology design course at the University of Twente. In this film we stage the Citroen DS as an Goddess actress of  many qualities placed in an ever changing worldly landscape against a background of famous high-rise structures and towers. Of course the famous French loaf and Camembert cheese can\'t be missed playing roles as archetypes of French Culture along with the Goddess.\n\n[vimeo 4891459]','So Many Dreams, So Many IDeas, So Many DS\'s...','','inherit','open','open','','650-autosave','','','2013-03-28 12:43:52','2013-03-28 12:43:52','',650,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=1436',0,'revision','',0),
