(1445,7,'2013-03-28 12:44:57','2013-03-28 12:44:57','On March 17th, 2010 the RSFF [re]search group visited Landre Werkmetaal in Vianen for a demonstration of multi-layered manufacturing using the V-Flash 3D printing technology. We sent a STL file of a raw shaped Virtual Clay model to Landre the night before to witness the results the next day at their location in Vianen. The V-Flash gave some good results and especially the speed and affordability are interesting aspects of instant prototyping during RSFF. Shown are some of the raw virtual models and results of the 3d raw models during and after printing. Further included are some other examples of rapid prototyping made with the V-Flash and Projet 3000 3D printers. We\'d like to thank Landre Werkmetaal BV for their support and demos. For more information: <a title=\"blocked::http://www.landre-werkmetaal.com/\" href=\"http://www.landre-werkmetaal.com/\">www.landre-werkmetaal.com</a>\n\n<img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/RAW_Shaping_DSTestCase4.jpg\" /><img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/autootje.jpg\" /><img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/autootje_mesh3_logo.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre01.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre03.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre7.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre29.jpg\" /><img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre31.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre37x.jpg\" /><img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre35.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre19.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Landre04.jpg\" /> <img src=\" http://www.rawshapin