(1955,7,'2017-10-23 09:26:13','2017-10-23 09:26:13','<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1951\" src=\"http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/IMG_20171020_115623109_HDR-350x350.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"385\" height=\"385\" />\r\n\r\nTheme: Hybrid Design Tools\r\nFaculty &amp; University: Faculty of Engineering Technology, University of Twente\r\nProjectowner: Robert E. Wendrich, Rawshaping Technology\r\nE-mail: r.e.wendrich@utwente.nl | info@rawshaping.com\r\nResearcher: Robert E. Wendrich\r\nStudents: Olaf Grevenstuk, Arno van Dijk, Simone Hesseling, Sander Hetebrij\r\nPartners: Frontwise (Werner Helmich)\r\nWebsite: www.rawshaping.com | playgora.nl\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PLAYGORA: Designing for Real</strong>\r\nGeïndividualiseerd design in combinatie met hybride (analoog-digitaal) ontwerpgereedschappen kan\r\nals ontbrekende schakel fungeren tussen mens, maatschappij en technologie. De PLAYGORA design\r\nomgeving introduceert vernieuwende interactieve oplossingen en gereedschappen om betekenisvolle\r\ncommunicatie, ervaringen, persoonlijke betrokkenheid en sociale-inclusie tot stand te brengen binnen\r\ndiverse contexten en variabele domeinen.\r\n<strong>PLAYGORA: Designing for Real</strong>\r\nIndividualised design combined with hybrid design tools, have the capacity to act as the missing link\r\nbetween humans, society, and technology. The PLAYGORA design environment entails innovative\r\ninteractive software solutions and design tools to create meaningful communication, experiences,\r\npersonal involvement and social inclusion within various contexts and/or domains.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1954\" src=\"http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/lfds-light-render2-350x350.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\r\nLink: <a href=\"http://www.mindthestep.nl/playgora.html\">http://www.mindthestep.nl/playgora.html</a>\r\n\r\nWebsite: <a href=\"http://www.play