ds/2019/03/Tosca-II-logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"210\" height=\"93\" /></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2062 \" src=\"http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-TOSCA-II-BOWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"702\" height=\"404\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-2067 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/P5250103-350x350.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">© 2019 All Rights Reserved</p>\r\nhttp://www.carlofelicegenova.it/2018/07/02/tosca/\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','TOSCA@RST','','inherit','closed','closed','','2054-revision-v1','','','2019-03-21 15:30:48','2019-03-21 15:30:48','',2054,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=2071',0,'revision','',0),
