(2048,7,'2019-03-21 11:05:54','2019-03-21 11:05:54','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2051 size-full\" src=\"http://www.rawshaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/EG_banner_1010x220-e1553166457418.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"109\" />\r\n\r\nEurographics 2019, the 40th Annual Conference of the <a href=\"http://www.eg.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">European Association for Computer Graphics</a>, will take place from May 6-10 in Genoa, Italy. It is organized by <a href=\"http://www.imati.cnr.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">IMATI CNR</a>. Eurographics 2019 is a unique platform for the computer graphics community to showcase latest techniques and educational work, and to explore new trends and ideas.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.eurographics2019.it/\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Industrial presentations &amp; exhibition</h3>\r\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">This year\'s event will be your opportunity to gain visibility for your technologies, research endeavors and services, as well as to advertise your company and technologies to the best researchers, professionals and students in the field. We would like to invite you to become active part of EG19 as a contributor and/or exhibitor. If you need further information about the event or the participation options we offer, or suggestions how to become part of EG19, please contact:  <a href=\"mailto:chairs-eg2019ind@eg.org\">chairs-eg2019ind@eg.org</a>.</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" align=\"justify\">Or for more information, please follow link:</p>\r\nhttps://www.eurographics2019.it/index.php/for-submitters/industrial-presentations/\r\n\r\n</div>','RST@Eurographics2019','','publish','open','closed','','rsteurographics2019','','','2019-03-21 11:26:19','2019-03-21 11:26:19','',0,'http://www.rawshaping.com/?p=2048',0,'post','',0),
